Replace `ACCOUNT_ID` with your real AWS account ID.

```json
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "DenyAdminUpdateInvoke",
      "Effect": "Deny",
      "Action": "lambda:InvokeFunction",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:lambda:us-east-1:ACCOUNT_ID:function:*ADMIN*UPDATE*ORDERS*"
    }
  ]
}
